    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "A.   Component 1. Design and Construction of Cyber Bureau The objective of this component is to construct the office building for Cyber Bureau of MoHA (Nepal Police) which shall comprehensively provide Cybercrime investigation, Digital forensic, and relevant training. B.   Component 2. Provision of the equipment The objective of this component is to equip the newly established Cyber Bureau with the package of equipment for Cybercrime investigation and Digital Forensic Lab including necessary office furniture. C.   Component 3. Capacity Building The objective of this component is to secure sustainable development of the Project by capacity building for Cyber Bureau."
